<section class="about">
    <div class="decoration">!</div>

    <div class="about-left">
        <h2 class="section-title">About<br>Me</h2>
        
        <div class="text-box">
            <h3 class="box-title">Content Creation</h3>
            <p>Hi, I’m Deeva! I’m a food, travel, and lifestyle content creator based in Canada, and a law student with a deep love for storytelling.</p>
            <p>What began as a passion project quickly grew into a community that values honest, relatable content. I’ve partnered with both global brands and small businesses, always with the same goal: to share experiences in a way that feels raw, real, and true to life.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-box secondary-box">
            <h3 class="box-title">Blog</h3>
            <p>My blog aims to take readers on a journey through flavors, cultures, and hidden gems. From "Asian pantry essentials" to "Best Cities to Visit in Italy," I blend personal experiences with expert recommendations, making every meal and trip unforgettable.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-right">
        <img src="/deeva-pfp.jpeg" alt="Photo of Deeva" class="creator-image-container">
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .about {
        background-color: var(--clr-cream);
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 100px 5%;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
        gap: 60px;
        align-items: start;
        color: var(--clr-blue);
    }

    .decoration {
        position: absolute;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 20rem;
        color: rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.08);
        right: -50px;
        bottom: -100px;
        z-index: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .about-left {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7.5vw, 7.5rem);
        line-height: 1;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--clr-blue);
        -webkit-text-stroke: 3px var(--clr-orange);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .text-box {
        background-color: var(--clr-white);
        color: var(--clr-blue);
        padding: 30px;
        border: 4px solid var(--clr-red);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-weight: 700;
        position: relative;
        box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px var(--clr-orange);
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .secondary-box {
        border-color: var(--clr-orange);
        box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px var(--clr-red);
    }

    .box-title {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--clr-red);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .secondary-box .box-title {
        color: var(--clr-orange);
    }

    .about-right {
        position: relative;
        margin-top: 60px;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .creator-image-container {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 3/4;
        background-color: var(--clr-red);
        border: 5px solid var(--clr-gold);
        position: sticky;
        top: 100px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .about {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            padding: 60px 5%;
        }
        .about-right {
            order: -1; 
        }
        .creator-image-container {
            max-width: 350px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: static;
        }
    }
</style>